data.description: Introducing your dream home! This spacious 4-bedroom, 3-bath gem boasts 1,864 square feet of elegant living space. Step inside to discover a captivating open concept design, perfect for entertaining. The heart of this home features a cozy fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. As you explore, you'll be enchanted by the beauty of the lush backyard, an oasis of tranquility with endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment. Whether it's morning coffee on the patio or evening cookouts, this backyard is your private retreat. With easy access to shopping, hospitals, and Loop 375. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house yours. Schedule your private viewing today.
